but I didn't believe it.

587
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:24,960
Did you really have an affair
with an outsider?

588
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:26,390
Father,

589
00:28:26,550 --> 00:28:27,390
I didn't.

590
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:29,550
Then who was that man talking
with you just now?

591
00:28:30,270 --> 00:28:31,350
Tempting a chaste widow

592
