and dismembering if he were captured.

594
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:39,240
Father,

595
00:28:41,310 --> 00:28:42,240
it's my fault.

596
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:44,400
I failed my duties as a woman

597
00:28:44,550 --> 00:28:45,880
and went out without permission.

598
00:28:46,070 --> 00:28:47,560
It has nothing to do with anyone else.

599
00:28:48,070 --> 00:28:49,400
Father, please discern the truth.

600
00:28:49,750 --> 00:28:51,160
You're still making excuses for him.

601
00:28:51,590 --> 00:28:53,000
You can't even protect yourself.

602
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:55,040
- Come.
- Stop.

603
00:28:59,830 --> 00:29:01,350
My Lord, it was me

604
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,030
who forced Mrs. Deng to meet me.

605
00:29:03,030 --> 00:29:03,920
It's my fault.

606
00:29:04,310 --> 00:29:05,200
No, Father.

607
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:06,040
Cheng Lei...

608
00:29:07,350 --> 00:29:08,190
You...

609
00:29:08,590 --> 00:29:09,430
So,

610
00:29:09,750 --> 00:29:11,030
this obscene book

611
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:13,270
was your secret connection?

612
00:29:13,750 --> 00:29:15,270
- No, Father.
- Have you no shame?

613
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:16,670
- Father.
- Shut up.

614
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:19,310
You shameless, immoral woman.

615
00:29:20,550 --> 00:29:22,590
Mr. Deng, what is a woman's duty?

616
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:31,640
Why is it that a widower can remarry

617
00:29:32,270 --> 00:29:33,680
but a widow can't?

618
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:36,270
Why can men have multiple concubines,

619
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:39,440
but women must be loyal
to one man forever?

620
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:42,110
Why is a man's flirtation praised,

621
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:45,000
while a woman seeking happiness

622
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:47,270
is nailed to the pillar of shame?

623
00:29:47,790 --> 00:29:48,790
We're all human.

624
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:51,070
Are women born
to suppress their desires?

625
00:29:51,310 --> 00:29:53,440
If this is your so-called women's duty,

626
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:56,240
then there's no need to carry it out.

627
00:29:58,400 --> 00:30:00,350
Zhuang Hanyan, it's you again.

628
00:30:00,750 --> 00:30:02,160
It must've been you

629
00:30:02,270 --> 00:30:04,590
who instigated them to commit adultery

630
00:30:04,730 --> 00:30:06,050
and ruin my family's reputation.

631
00:30:06,110 --> 00:30:07,750
You wicked woman.

632
00:30:08,160 --> 00:30:10,750
Before you got married,

633
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:13,750
I could tell you were no good.

634
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:15,920
Now, after marrying Mr. Fu,

635
00:30:16,030 --> 00:30:18,270
you often show yourself
in public, ruining morals.

636
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:20,310
If Fu Yunxi refuses to discipline you,

637
00:30:20,310 --> 00:30:23,030
I will do it for him.

638
00:30:27,790 --> 00:30:29,280
- Mother.
- You...

639
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:30,240
Chan.

640
00:30:31,030 --> 00:30:31,870
Mr. Deng,

641
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:33,270
a couple is united as one.

642
00:30:33,270 --> 00:30:34,350
Are you going

643
00:30:35,110 --> 00:30:36,830
to slap me in the face?

644
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:38,880
Fine.

645
00:30:39,070 --> 00:30:40,640
The public morals are falling apart.

646
00:30:41,510 --> 00:30:43,440
Rituals and laws are doomed.

647
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,040
Chan.

648
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:47,520
Grandfather,

649
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:49,830
for the sake of my mother's years

650
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:52,160
of loyal service to our family,

651
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:54,040
please

652
00:30:54,590 --> 00:30:55,460
spare her.

653
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,070
You're also defending her?

654
00:30:57,070 --> 00:30:58,160
Are you also going to become

655
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,640
a shameless, immoral women like her?

656
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:00,480
I...

657
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,960
Chan, Chan.

658
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:04,640
Let me see it.

659
00:31:07,550 --> 00:31:09,480
If my daughter had a choice,

660
00:31:14,110 --> 00:31:15,880
I'd rather

661
00:31:19,350 --> 00:31:20,440
she never became

662
00:31:21,290 --> 00:31:22,900
a good woman like I was,

663
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:26,790
praised by everyone.

664
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:29,960
Zhang,

665
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:31,440
how dare you speak

666
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:33,030
such reckless words?

667
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,790
I just spoke the truth,

668
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:41,750
and you can't bear it?

669
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:44,640
Get up, Chan.

670
00:31:48,750 --> 00:31:49,590
Today,

671
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:53,070
let me tell you all the truth.

672
00:31:54,510 --> 00:31:55,880
It's been 17 years.

673
00:31:57,310 --> 00:31:59,550
I've never missed

674
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:01,200
my late husband day and night

675
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:04,200
and adhered to a woman's duty.

676
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:08,000
I never truly loved your son.

677
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:11,200
I've even forgotten what he looks like.

678
00:32:11,790 --> 00:32:13,590
- You...
- Between him and me,

679
00:32:14,110 --> 00:32:15,750
there was never any warmth or affection.

680
00:32:17,350 --> 00:32:18,830
He despised my poetry and literature

681
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:21,200
and burned my books.

682
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:22,920
But I know

683
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:25,550
he was just jealous

684
00:32:26,550 --> 00:32:27,830
and afraid.

685
00:32:29,790 --> 00:32:31,790
He was a mediocre man

686
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,750
who was born

687
00:32:33,750 --> 00:32:35,920
into a scholarly family like yours.

688
00:32:36,270 --> 00:32:37,110
You...

689
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:39,840
Do you know?

690
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:42,830
The essays of your son

691
00:32:43,680 --> 00:32:45,070
that you highly praised

692
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:47,830
were written

693
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:50,200
by me.

694
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:54,160
He stole my talent

695
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,160
while suppressing me.

696
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:58,310
Whenever he felt inferior,

697
00:32:58,880 --> 00:33:00,550
he would ignore and torment me.

698
00:33:00,550 --> 00:33:02,000
I've had enough.

699
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:04,020
I don't want to endure this any longer.

700
00:33:05,030 --> 00:33:06,510
I've had enough.

701
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,550
Nonsense.

702
00:33:08,680 --> 00:33:10,700
How can you accuse my son without proof?

703
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:13,440
You can't believe the words
of a shameless woman.

704
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:14,510
What is a shameless woman?

705
00:33:14,530 --> 00:33:16,840
If breaking free from chains
makes me a shameless woman,

706
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,700
and trapping myself
makes me a virtuous woman,

707
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:21,350
what's wrong with being
a shameless women?

708
00:33:21,350 --> 00:33:22,190
You...

709
00:33:24,830 --> 00:33:26,270
It's been 17 years.

710
00:33:26,440 --> 00:33:27,680
I've sacrificed

711
00:33:28,270 --> 00:33:29,880
17 years of my life.

712
00:33:32,750 --> 00:33:35,070
For an empty reputation,

713
00:33:35,830 --> 00:33:37,000
I've locked myself

714
00:33:38,110 --> 00:33:39,440
in a cage

715
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:43,270
called chastity.

716
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:46,400
I've been tied to it
like it's part of my flesh,

717
00:33:47,110 --> 00:33:48,510
and it's hard for me to break free.

718
00:33:49,640 --> 00:33:50,550
But today,

719
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:55,550
I no longer wish

720
00:33:58,790 --> 00:33:59,960
to keep that chastity plaque

721
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:02,920
for you

722
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:08,400
and for your vanity.

723
00:34:09,350 --> 00:34:11,790
I want to reclaim my name.

724
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:20,480
My name is Zhang Wanjun,

725
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:21,880
the eldest daughter

726
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:23,710
of the Zhang family

727
00:34:25,590 --> 00:34:26,550
in Jiying Alley.

728
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:31,510
For my brother's career,

729
00:34:33,710 --> 00:34:35,550
for the prosperity of my family,

730
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:39,710
and

731
00:34:40,710 --> 00:34:42,030
for my children's future,

732
00:34:43,030 --> 00:34:44,590
I've endured for many years.

733
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:46,360
But today,

734
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:51,440
I want to live for myself.

735
00:34:54,070 --> 00:34:56,630
I want to live well.

736
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:58,030
You've gone mad.

737
00:34:59,190 --> 00:35:00,230
You've gone mad.

738
00:35:00,230 --> 00:35:02,230
Yes, I've gone mad.

739
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:04,550
For 17 years,

740
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:07,710
I've shaped myself into a revered,

741
00:35:08,630 --> 00:35:10,630
untouchable figure.

742
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:11,840
Today,

743
00:35:11,840 --> 00:35:14,070
I'm going to shatter that figure
with my own hands.

744
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:16,360
Even if it breaks,

745
00:35:18,630 --> 00:35:20,070
I can still piece it together.

746
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:23,840
I can do it.

747
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:26,710
I can do this.

748
00:35:32,110 --> 00:35:33,480
Even if I'm bleeding

749
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:35,800
and covered in wounds,

750
00:35:36,400 --> 00:35:37,960
as long as my name remains,

751
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:42,840
I am

752
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:46,510
a complete woman.

753
00:35:47,150 --> 00:35:48,840
Why can't I

754
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,210
have someone who understands me,

755
00:35:52,880 --> 00:35:53,720
respects me,

756
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:56,550
and cherishes me to love me?

757
00:35:58,030 --> 00:35:59,110
Why can't I?

758
00:36:01,150 --> 00:36:02,280
Why can't I

759
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:03,240
live without fear

760
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:06,550
for once?

761
00:36:07,590 --> 00:36:08,430
Someone.

762
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,280
The madam is delirious,

763
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,400
speaking nonsense.

764
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:13,000
Take her back immediately,

765
00:36:13,090 --> 00:36:14,310
and confine her for treatment.

766
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:16,280
Take the young lady back
and watch over her.

767
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:18,300
Tomorrow, she'll get married
at an auspicious time.

768
00:36:18,630 --> 00:36:21,070
Whoever obstructs my family affairs

769
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:23,230
will face my wrath.

770
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:24,680
Go.

771
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:27,000
- Grandfather, I won't marry him.
- Go.

772
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,670
- No.
- I won't marry him.

773
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:29,710
I'm not afraid.

774
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:30,710
I won't marry her.

775
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:33,360
I love only Chan Zhixue.

776
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:35,320
Let me go.

777
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:36,630
Let me go.

778
00:36:46,860 --> 00:36:50,820
(Deng Mansion)

779
00:37:27,940 --> 00:37:29,940
(Wedding procession, Zheng Mansion)

780
00:37:31,230 --> 00:37:32,010
- This...
- Master.

781
00:37:32,030 --> 00:37:32,770
Master, bad news.

782
00:37:32,770 --> 00:37:34,060
The inner chambers are on fire.

783
00:37:34,150 --> 00:37:34,990
Let's go.

784
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:54,840
Go fetch water. Water!

785
00:37:55,190 --> 00:37:56,960
The imperial edict is in her room.

786
00:37:57,190 --> 00:37:58,630
The edict is important.

787
00:37:58,760 --> 00:38:00,150
Put out the fire.

788
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:10,230
Mr. Deng,

789
00:38:11,190 --> 00:38:12,960
if you want peace in your home,

790
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:15,110
the fire you truly need to extinguish

791
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:16,760
is the stubborn,

792
00:38:17,030 --> 00:38:18,840
obsessive fire in your heart.

793
00:38:19,190 --> 00:38:20,030
It's you.

794
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:22,790
You let her go.

795
00:38:23,190 --> 00:38:25,840
From now on, there won't no Mrs. Deng

796
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,920
or the student Cheng Lei in this world.

797
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:29,880
When did you let her go?

798
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:32,480
Where are all my servants?

799
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:34,880
I've served
in the Judicial Review for years.

800
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:37,070
This is just a piece of cake

801
00:38:38,710 --> 00:38:39,590
for me.

802
00:38:41,510 --> 00:38:42,590
Fu Yunxi,

803
00:38:44,150 --> 00:38:46,070
you and your wife are very bold.

804
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:47,710
Don't you fear

805
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:49,880
being imprisoned or executed?

806
00:38:50,510 --> 00:38:51,670
Your chaste daughter-in-law,

807
00:38:52,230 --> 00:38:53,360
after receiving praise,

808
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:56,190
remembered her late husband
with deep sorrow,

809
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:58,760
so today, she set herself on fire

810
00:38:59,190 --> 00:39:00,280
to join him in death.

811
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:01,680
Is Noble Consort Miao

812
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:05,110
behind all of this?

813
00:39:05,630 --> 00:39:07,030
It's an act for the sake of justice.

814
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:08,880
No one is behind it.

815
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:12,360
What crime have I committed?

816
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:15,230
Would the heavens destroy me too?

817
00:39:15,230 --> 00:39:17,230
You knew the importance
of a woman's reputation,

818
00:39:17,630 --> 00:39:19,880
yet you still insisted on tarnishing

819
00:39:20,670 --> 00:39:22,550
the name of an innocent childless woman

820
00:39:22,550 --> 00:39:24,110
in the Palace.

821
00:39:24,630 --> 00:39:25,510
Is this

822
00:39:26,510 --> 00:39:27,710
not a crime?

823
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,630
Mr. Deng, you've repeatedly said

824
00:39:32,070 --> 00:39:33,800
that you must protect your family's

825
00:39:33,960 --> 00:39:35,530
long-standing reputation and foundation

826
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:37,960
even if you're shattered to pieces

827
00:39:38,150 --> 00:39:40,630
and have to die for principles.

828
00:39:40,630 --> 00:39:42,630
Zhang Wanjun has left the Capital,

829
00:39:42,630 --> 00:39:44,480
and her name for chastity and virtue

830
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:46,960
should be burned clean

831
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:48,510
in this fire.

832
00:39:48,510 --> 00:39:49,350
No, no, no.

833
00:39:49,550 --> 00:39:50,390
I'll tell you.

834
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:51,590
I'll tell you everything.

835
00:39:52,480 --> 00:39:53,320
We're all ears.

836
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:55,280
I know that everything you've done

837
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:56,760
is to help Noble Consort Miao,

838
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:59,440
but there's no need to involve others.

839
00:39:59,670 --> 00:40:01,000
So, who should we involve?

840
00:40:01,230 --> 00:40:03,550
Only one man is to be blamed for this.

841
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:04,710
The others

842
00:40:04,710 --> 00:40:07,030
only did some paperwork.

843
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:09,320
The one who wants
to kill Noble Consort Miao

844
00:40:09,320 --> 00:40:10,960
is Yao Zhidong, Grand Secretary

845
00:40:12,040 --> 00:40:13,280
of the Hall of Literary Glory.

846
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:16,840
What I can do

847
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:18,510
is withdraw from this petition.

848
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:19,680
But Mr. Yao

849
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:21,480
